        <heading>687.  Person doing business under trade name</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 687.  Person doing business under trade name
A person who does business under a trade name shall sue in his own name to enforce a right created by or arising out of the doing of such business.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
